plyTime":"2017-04-22T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"好似幾有趣 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d594d7498387be7529d060ff384dbc2ce069aa","tid":212262,"uid":84442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:17:55.000Z","msg":"靈魂學說<br />\n會唔會係因為人類接受唔到自己單純被肉體支配而得出既學說呢<br />\n始終靈魂完全冇科學證據支持"},{"pid":"5d15845f7bee1b95ed2074a83bc768e546415d51","tid":212262,"uid":84442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:23:00.000Z","msg":"再退一步來說<br />\n假設有靈魂<br />\n靈魂又如何令人類擁有情感 記憶等等呢?<br />\n會唔會係靈魂只不過係某種特別的物質 無色無味 取代左肉體既功能?<br />\n咁樣算唔算另類肉體呢"},{"pid":"b84a9566b94cbd3f7e082250238169a21661a2fc","tid":212262,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再退一步來說<br />\n假設有靈魂<br />\n靈魂又如何令人類擁有情感 記憶等等呢?<br />\n會唔會係靈魂只不過係某種特別的物質 無色無味 取代左肉體既功能?<br />\n咁樣算唔算另類肉體呢</blockquote><br />\n你搵 阿含經 童女迦葉 入面問問題果個同你問既一樣"},{"pid":"58c1e5e017902fc9efe54b7949342a22c42ecb3e","tid":212262,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:33:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ctworld.org.tw/sutra_stories/story209.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctworld.org.tw%2Fsutra_stories%2Fstory209.htm&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e5523a0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctworld.org.tw/sutra_stories/story209.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f3472bd9ecbbb4c1e779449b4e2447a4d00a7fb1","tid":212262,"uid":84442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.ctworld.org.tw/sutra_stories/story209.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctworld.org.tw%2Fsutra_stories%2Fstory209.htm&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e5523a0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctworld.org.tw/sutra_stories/story209.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n你指呢段 弊宿說：「沙門說：人有識神...?<br />\n佢好似只